Summary from Congitive Biases & The Questions YOu Shouldn't be Asking

Ask questions like - 
# Just to be sure I'm clear - if you had that already, how would it make your job/life easier?
# Since you don't have it today what's your current workaround?
# In the last 6 months, how often has [situation] happened?
# You're right, [competitor] does offer this feature. I'd love to hear your impression of their solution...
# You mentioned it might come in handy in future - how areyou anticipating your needs changing?
# If you could wave a magic wand and change ANYTHING about [situation] - doesn't have to be possible - what would it be?
